title: Directs the N.Y. state Thruway Authority to discontinue the New Rochelle toll plaza on the New England section of the state thruway
summary: Directs the NYS Thruway Authority to discontinue the New Rochelle toll plaza on the New England section of the state thruway.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the public authorities law, in relation to discontinuing the New Rochelle toll plaza on the New England section of the New York state thruway
